The Keiser Report (Russia Today) No. 92
- Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert -
Thursday, 04 November 2010


[sebaygo1]


Fake Markets! Fake Finance! Scandal! 

Max and Stacy look at the scandals of fake judges using fake deputies to collect fake debts in fake courts and of Irish austerity under imposed under fake pretences. 

In the second half of the show Max talks to David McWilliams about Ireland's first ever economics festival, Kilkenomics, and the financial and banking crisis that inspired it.




The .mp3 is audio extracted from the Russia Today video.
